text: Cristian Bățagă (born 10 April 1988) is a Romanian gymnast. He competed in four events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Târgu Mureș Category:European Games competitors for Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 2015 European Games
